{"meta":{"title":"2 Néphi 22","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/22?lang=fra","contentType":"text/html","pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"d937d8d6f8f45918992ca4571e1fae238f121241","data-aid":"117850488","data-aid-version":"5","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/22","lang":"fra","data-orig-id":"9dd17b233089cb6c8ac17bf4061b02fc027c45df","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"2 Néphi 22","description":"Pendant l’ère millénaire tous les hommes loueront le Seigneur — Il demeurera parmi eux — Comparez avec Ésaïe 12. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"2 Néphi 22","description":"Pendant l’ère millénaire tous les hommes loueront le Seigneur — Il demeurera parmi eux — Comparez avec Ésaïe 12. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"117850489\" id=\"title_number1\">Chapitre 22</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"117850490\" id=\"study_summary1\">Pendant l’ère millénaire tous les hommes loueront le Seigneur — Il demeurera parmi eux — Comparez avec <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/12?lang=fra\">Ésaïe 12</a>. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850491\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Tu diras en ce jour-là : Je te loue, ô Seigneur ! Car tu as été irrité contre moi, ta colère s’est apaisée, et tu m’as consolé.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850492\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Voici, Dieu est ma délivrance, je serai <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>plein</a> de confiance, et je ne craindrai rien ; car le Seigneur, le <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>Seigneur</a> est ma force et le sujet de mes louanges ; c’est lui qui m’a sauvé.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850493\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Vous puiserez de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>l’eau</a> avec joie aux sources du salut,</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850494\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>et vous direz en ce jour-là : <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>louez</a> le Seigneur, invoquez son nom, publiez ses œuvres parmi les peuples, rappelez la grandeur de son nom !</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850495\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Célébrez</a> le Seigneur, car il a fait des choses magnifiques : qu’elles soient connues par toute la terre !</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117850496\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note6a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>Pousse</a> des cris de joie et d’allégresse, habitant de Sion ! Car il est grand au milieu de toi, le Saint d’Israël.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"22\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850497\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.6?lang=fra#p6\">Mos 4:6</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1?lang=fra#p1\">Hél 12:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850498\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/15.2?lang=fra#p2\">Ex 15:2</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/83.19?lang=fra#p19\">Ps 83:19</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/jehovah?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Jéhovah</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850499\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/living-water?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Eau vive</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850500\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/thankful-thanks-thanksgiving?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Reconnaissance, reconnaissant</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850501\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/136.28?lang=fra#p28\">D&amp;A 136:28</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117850502\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/54.1?lang=fra#p1\">És 54:1</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.14?lang=fra#p14\">So 3:14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"117850492","context":"plein","text":"<p data-aid=\"117850497\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.6?lang=fra#p6\">Mos 4:6</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1?lang=fra#p1\">Hél 12:1</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.6?lang=fra#p6","text":"Mos 4:6"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.1?l